ISLAMABAD, Mar 8 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Tuesday that Prime Minister Imran Khan was the only political leader of the country.
In a tweet, he dared the pigmies of the opposition to join hands and make an effort but he said  the political dwarfs were destined to face defeat.
